title: Moving To LA & Losing $13,000 (John Castro)
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
itunes:summary:
Ilya's best friend John joins us, he just moved to Los Angeles under a fun circumstance and we dive into moving here from the Philippines not knowing English, seeing snow for the first time, losing $13,000 in the stock game, and more. Thanks for tuning in and enjoy our episode with our buddy John

Follow John online at @doesjohnevenhaveaninsta

Follow us on instagram @lightweightspod
